Agentless Universal Shutdown
============================

Installation GNU/Linux
----------------------

Required packages:
 - Event
 - Proc::Daemon
 - Sys::Syslog
 - XML::LibXML
 - Linux::Inotify2
 
Optional:
 - VMware::VIRuntime (VMware 3.5)
 - RPC::XML          (Xen 5.0)
 - RPC::XML::Client  (Xen 5.0)


